    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think that what is expected to be numeric should be parsed. The reason is that we have a serialized form that may cause the number to be transformed to string (url stuff) but for the sake of convenience we should provide numbers when we can (who wants to parse a value coming from a library?)\n\nI'm fixing the bug you found @Jerskouille. I couldn't find the ticket on the helper, if there is one, can you reference it here?\n",
